Update Stored Document

Call the `{{tool_prefix}}document_update` tool:

```
{{tool_prefix}}document_update(
    category="{{args.0.value}}",
    name="{{args.1.value}}"{{#kwargs.new_name}},
    new_name="{{kwargs.new_name}}"{{/kwargs.new_name}}{{#kwargs.new_category}},
    new_category="{{kwargs.new_category}}"{{/kwargs.new_category}}{{#kwargs.metadata_add}},
    metadata_add={{kwargs.metadata_add}}{{/kwargs.metadata_add}}{{#kwargs.metadata_replace}},
    metadata_replace={{kwargs.metadata_replace}}{{/kwargs.metadata_replace}}{{#kwargs.metadata_clear}},
    metadata_clear={{kwargs.metadata_clear}}{{/kwargs.metadata_clear}}
)
```

{{#kwargs.metadata_add}}Parse the metadata-add value as a JSON dict before passing it to the tool.{{/kwargs.metadata_add}}
{{#kwargs.metadata_replace}}Parse the metadata-replace value as a JSON dict before passing it to the tool.{{/kwargs.metadata_replace}}
{{#kwargs.metadata_clear}}Parse the metadata-clear value as a comma-separated list of keys.{{/kwargs.metadata_clear}}
